      "content": "wow that's a really powerful way to put it. you're saying it's basically just a way to hide privilege. if i were to write a conclusion that summarizes the whole thing, how would you wrap it up to make the reader feel like there’s really no other moral choice here besides supporting these redistribution policies? like, how do i make it clear that the alternative is just accepting injustice?",
